Pete Godbole

I think in our prepared remarks, Melissa, we referenced the three things. We talked about less macroeconomic headwinds. We talked about the volume of larger transactions and the strong sales execution. Those were absolutely the case. We sort of covered those fairly well. I would say a couple of things we expanded across almost every vertical. Our sales time – our sales cycle time has reduced and our pipeline conversion improved all in line with the earlier comments I made.

