Mark Mader

Yes. I think there are a couple of items. One is, I think a more refined look and feel, but there's also a huge part of that, which is around discoverability, right. We have this ever-growing set of capabilities unless you can have your users unlock those and benefit from them, they somewhat don't matter. So we're really looking forward to being able to make certain things much more obvious. And again, over the years, we've added a lot to the product and now our job is not only to build, but to also make sure that there's full attach across the suite and that's really what we're aiming to do.

